title: Teriyaki Chicken Bowl
description: Grilled chicken served on a bed of rice with teriyaki sauce, steamed vegetables, and sesame seeds.

title: Margherita Pizza
description: A classic pizza topped with tomato sauce, mozzarella cheese, and fresh basil.

title: Beef Burger
description: A juicy beef patty topped with lettuce, tomato, onion, and your choice of cheese. Served with fries.

title: Pad Thai
description: Stir-fried rice noodles with shrimp, tofu, bean sprouts, and peanuts in a tangy tamarind sauce.

title: BBQ Ribs
description: Fall-off-the-bone tender pork ribs smothered in BBQ sauce, served with coleslaw and fries.

title: Caesar Salad
description: Crisp romaine lettuce with shaved parmesan cheese, croutons, and a creamy Caesar dressing.

title: Miso Soup
description: A traditional Japanese soup made with miso paste, tofu, seaweed, and scallions.

title: Fish Tacos
description: Grilled fish, shredded cabbage, and a tangy sauce in soft tortillas, served with rice and beans.

title: Chicken Alfredo
description: Fettuccine pasta in a creamy Alfredo sauce with grilled chicken, mushrooms, and garlic.

title: Falafel Wrap
description: A warm pita filled with crispy falafel, lettuce, tomato, cucumber, and tahini sauce.
